                                                                                                                                                                             (NICE FRAMEWORK)

                                                                                               Users may also create entirely new Task, Knowledge, or Skill statements to help tailor the use of
                                                                                               the NICE Framework for local use within their unique context. Such additional statements will
                                                                                               help support clear and consistent internal discussions regarding learners and their work activities.

                                                                                               3.3   Competencies

                                                                                               Competencies provide a mechanism for organizations to assess            Competency
                                                                                               learners. Competencies are defined via an employer-driven               A mechanism for
                                                                                               approach that provides insight to an organization’s unique              organizations to assess
                                                                                               context. Furthermore, Competencies allow education and                  learners.
                                                                                               training providers to be responsive to employer or sector needs
                                                                                               by developing learning experiences that help learners develop           Competencies are
